<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
  <h1 style="color: #dc3545; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;">
    Application Rejected
  </h1>
</div>

<div style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Dear <strong><%= companyName || 'Applicant' %></strong>,
  </p>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Thank you for your interest in joining Canadian Bazaar as a seller. After careful review of your application, 
    we regret to inform you that we are unable to approve your seller account at this time.
  </p>

  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3 style="color: #dc3545; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 18px;">Reason for rejection:</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
      <%= rejectionReason || 'Application does not meet our current requirements' %>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #856404; margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 16px;">What you can do:</h4>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #856404;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Review our seller requirements and guidelines</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Address the issues mentioned in the rejection reason</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Gather any additional documentation that may be required</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Reapply once you have met all the requirements</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="border: 1px solid #d1ecf1; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #d1ecf1; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #0c5460; margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 16px;">Future Applications:</h4>
    <p style="margin: 0; color: #0c5460; font-size: 14px;">
      This rejection does not prevent you from reapplying in the future. We encourage you to address the 
      concerns mentioned above and submit a new application when you are ready. Each application is 
      reviewed individually and thoroughly.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="mailto:support@canadianbazaar.ca" 
       style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
      Contact Support
    </a>
  </div>

  <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    If you have any questions about this decision or need clarification on our requirements, 
    please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    Thank you for your understanding.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    Best regards,<br>
    <strong>Canadian Bazaar Admin Team</strong>
  </p>
</div>